spec_data.Name: python2-pytest-mock
spec_data.Description:
This plugin installs a mocker fixture which is a thin-wrapper around the
patching API provided by the mock package, but with the benefit of not having
to worry about undoing patches at the end of a test.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 16 Sep 2017 04:39:13 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Thin-wrapper around the mock package for easier use with py.test
